{"tid":1658262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞裔人士求下你地唔好再幫中共啦，唔想你地成為下一班蝗","createTime":"2019-10-16T12:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T12:43:27.000Z","uid":26087,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bbd21217d7b7b383e2c68d99e56fe5f0b0bf9384","tid":1658262,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"我唔知你地當初點解會過嚟香港定居，如果係為左有更好嘅生活，唔該你地勸下身邊嘅親朋戚友啦，你地再係咁幫中共打壓為左自由嘅人，好快要準備諗定去下一個國家。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係希望你地個個都為香港出錢出力，但最少可唔可以唔好幫呢啲極權政府打壓我地得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n我知道有唔少南亞裔人都係支持我地，希望你地可以勸下其他仲未醒仲想有自由嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797a954886c540f8bd0d458478d6b3bb63c40b07","tid":1658262,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d38a040a8cb71c9d1c19ee9c313da3240a2a60","tid":1658262,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5dd0775237db79d358ee40c0583fa76b5b332c9","tid":1658262,"uid":26087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"唔好因為咁而仇恨南亞人，有好多都係前線手足嚟，好多都仲博過香港人"},{"pid":"9bf69582e40992f45457b78aeb191151f3e74418","tid":1658262,"uid":133363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf564acc9a2cd3913801e517394352828411e05","tid":1658262,"uid":238966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:42:29.000Z","msg":"有一班就只會認錢唔認人 醒啦樓主 現實就係咁"},{"pid":"db2e1f0ac1e149bf52b357c1d1ae3bb875c2c98d","tid":1658262,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母岑子杰單野我要響國際新聞見到！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658212</a>